{{> head}}
<body>
{{> header}}

<div class="w3-container w3-padding-64">
	<div class="owl-carousel owl-theme home-carousel">
	    <div class="item"><img src="/img/home_carousel/main1.jpg" /></div>
	    <div class="item"><img src="/img/home_carousel/main2.jpg" /></div>
      <div class="item"><img src="/img/home_carousel/main3.jpg" /></div>
      <div class="item"><img src="/img/home_carousel/main4.jpg" /></div>
      <div class="item"><img src="/img/home_carousel/main5.jpg" /></div>
	</div>
  <div>
    <h2>Welcome to Chadwell Dental Care LTD</h2>
    <p>Our practice has been serving the community for over seventy years, and we have carried on this tradition.</p>
    <p>We pride ourselves on providing good quality dentistry for all our patients, both NHS and private. We will listen to your needs and give you suitable options for treatment.</p>
    <p>We provide general dentistry from routine fillings to implants and orthodontics.</p>
    <p>As a family based practice, we see generations of the same family attending our practice, and welcome nervous patients.</p>
    <p>It is important for us to give you a good experience at our practice. A good experience for you is a good experience for us!</p>
  </div>
  <a href="/files/cqc_report.pdf" target="_blank" class="cqc-main">
      <div><img src="/img/cqc_logo.jpg" /><p>We take cross infection control procedures very seriously and were commended by the CQC. Please click here to read the report.</p></div>
  </a>
</div>

<div class="w3-row-padding w3-grayscale">
  <div class="w3-col l3 m6 w3-margin-bottom">
    <h3><i class="fa fa-clock-o"></i> Opening hours</h3>
    <p><strong>Mon, Tue, Wed, Fri: </strong>8:30-17:30</p>
    <p><strong>Thu: </strong>8:30-19:30</p>
    <p><strong>Sat, Sun: </strong>Closed</p>
    <p><strong>If you have an emergency outside our normal opening hours, please call 111 for NHS emergency services.</strong></p>
  </div>
  <div class="w3-col l3 m6 w3-margin-bottom">
    <h3><i class="fa fa-wheelchair"></i> Accessibility</h3>
    <p>The practice is on the ground floor and is fully accessible for the disabled.</p>
    <p>The building has been recently refurbished and all three surgeries have been purpose built with new equipment.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="w3-col l3 m6 w3-margin-bottom">
    <h3><i class="fa fa-calendar-check-o"></i> Appointments</h3>
    <p>To make an appointment, please give us a call or visit our reception.</p>
    <p>We provide both NHS and private dental treatment.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="w3-col l3 m6 w3-margin-bottom">
    <h3><i class="fa fa-star"></i> Commendations</h3>
    <div class="owl-carousel owl-theme commendation-carousel">
      {{#each commendations}}
        <div class="item">
          <blockquote>
            {{this.text}}
            <cite>- {{this.cite}}</cite>
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      {{/each}}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{{> footer}}
</body>